<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Password Reset Code - Shoppie</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f8fafc; color: #222; }
    .container { max-width: 480px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(44,90,160,0.08); padding: 32px 28px; }
    .logo { font-size: 1.6em; color: #2563eb; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .code-box { background: #f1f5f9; color: #2563eb; font-size: 2em; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 4px; border-radius: 8px; padding: 18px 0; text-align: center; margin: 24px 0 18px 0; }
    .footer { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.95em; margin-top: 32px; text-align: center; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 18px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">Shoppie</div>
    <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
    <p>Hello,</p>
    <p>We received a request to reset your password for your Shoppie account.</p>
    <p>Please use the code below to reset your password. This code is valid for <b>10 minutes</b>:</p>
    <div class="code-box"><%= code %></div>
    <p>If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Shoppie. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
